name: Ceramic Cup: Tea or coffee?
description:
A wheel thrown ceramic cup for unique pottery item lovers. Suitable for daily use. Drinking coffee/tea, serving jams, etc. limited with your creativity. 

Outside textured and inside wheat glazed. 
Height of body: 7cm, diameter: 8cm

All ceramics items are unique, only 1 of this item in stock.

Contact me for locations outside the AU.
